### Python Service API Requests
### So much cleaner than Java Spring Boot!
### Base URL: http://localhost:8001

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8001/health/

###

### 2. Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:8001/

###

### 3. Generate Student ID
POST http://localhost:8001/generate/student-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "school_id": 1
}

###

### 4. Generate Teacher ID  
POST http://localhost:8001/generate/teacher-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "school_id": 1
}

###

### 5. Get Next Sequences for School
GET http://localhost:8001/generate/next-sequences/1

###

### 6. API Documentation (automatic!)
GET http://localhost:8001/docs

###

### 7. Alternative docs
GET http://localhost:8001/redoc

###

### 8. School Analytics (placeholder)
GET http://localhost:8001/analytics/school/1